{"title":"三根金线","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":9,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"三根金线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔彝族〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从前——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心上有三根金线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根连在阿妈身上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根连在阿爹身上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根连在表哥身上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当阿妈挨鞭子的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心扯破了；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当阿爹被禾麻抽打的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心扯烂了；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当表哥被绳子绑走的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心啊，碎了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心上有三根金线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根连在毛主席身上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根连在共产党身上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根连在汉族老大哥身上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当毛主席说话的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心象琴弦一样响了；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当共产党说话的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心象火把一样亮了；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汉族老大哥帮我们建设家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心象大雁一样飞起来了。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}